  "page": "Feature quote/73",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“<a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> wants no <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasars</a></i> seething round our walls. The stench of all those horses... meaning no offense, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khaleesi\" title=\"Khaleesi\">Khaleesi</a></i>.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Xaro_Xhoan_Daxos\" title=\"Xaro Xhoan Daxos\">Xaro Xhoan Daxos</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404012143\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 63/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 330/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 528/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.078      1 -total\n100.00%    4.078      1 Template:Ref\n 60.99%    2.487      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw